org.ow2.proactive.scheduler.common.task

Class NativeTask

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ow2.proactive.scheduler.common.task.CommonAttribute
      • org.ow2.proactive.scheduler.common.task.Task
        • org.ow2.proactive.scheduler.common.task.NativeTask
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    @PublicAPI
public class NativeTask
extends Task
    Use this class to build a native task that will use a 'org.ow2.proactive.scheduler.task.NativeExecutable' and be integrated in a TaskFlowJob.

    A native task just includes a command line that can be set using setCommandLine(String[]).

    You don't have to extend this class to launch your own native executable.

    Since:
    ProActive Scheduling 0.9
    See Also:
